---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout
  title="about | human nature health"
  description="about the purpose and direction of human nature health."
>
  <section class="page-hero section">
    <div class="container narrow">
      <p class="eyebrow">about</p>
      <h1>this site exists to help people return to a healthier relationship with life.</h1>
      <p class="lead">
        the central idea is simple: many modern problems get worse when people become disconnected
        from sleep, light, real food, movement, calm, stillness, nature, and meaning.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <div class="container narrow">
      <div class="content-block">
        <h2>what this site values</h2>
        <p>
          clarity over confusion. grounded principles over hype. rhythms over extremes. health that
          includes mind, body, and the deeper inner life.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="content-block">
        <h2>what this site is becoming</h2>
        <p>
          a calm, growing archive of natural health guidance. not just content to consume, but ideas
          people can actually use to live better.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="content-block">
        <h2>where it is going</h2>
        <p>
          over time this will expand into deeper guides, practical pathways, and future resources
          that help people build healthier and happier lives in a way that feels real.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="quote-block">
        <p>
          better living usually begins with remembering what human beings actually need.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
  <section class="section">
    <div class="container narrow">
      <div class="y2k-panel feature-card">
        <div class="panel-heading-row">
          <p class="panel-kicker">principles</p>
          <span class="panel-stamp">core</span>
        </div>
        <h2>what this is built on</h2>
        <div class="content-list">
          <p>simple inputs create powerful outcomes</p>
          <p>health is physical, mental, and internal</p>
          <p>rhythm matters more than intensity</p>
          <p>consistency beats complexity</p>
          <p>nature is a reference point, not a trend</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
  <section class="section">
    <div class="container narrow">
      <div class="two-panel-grid">
        <a href="/start-here" class="y2k-panel feature-card">
          <p class="panel-kicker">previous</p>
          <h3>start here</h3>
          <p>return to the simple foundation and core path.</p>
        </a>

        <a href="/sleep" class="y2k-panel feature-card">
          <p class="panel-kicker">next</p>
          <h3>sleep</h3>
          <p>move into the foundation of recovery and rest.</p>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>